    "When the number of document retrieval is moderate, the model can effectively utilize the external knowledge base to achieve higher quality generated text, and perform well in reasoning tasks with complex background information.Although increasing the number of retrieved documents can improve the reasoning ability of the model to a certain extent, when the number of documents is too large, information redundancy will affect the generation quality and knowledge consistency, and the gain effect is limited.",
    "This shows that there is an optimal balance point for the amount of information retrieved, and beyond this point, the performance improvement of the model tends to be flat.",
